<section id="Section519936">
  <title>
<indexterm significance="normal">
      <primary>item sites</primary>
      <secondary>by class code</secondary>
    </indexterm>
<indexterm significance="normal">
      <primary>class codes</primary>
      <secondary>item site details for</secondary>
    </indexterm>Item Sites by Class Code</title>
  <para>To view Item Sites by Class Code, select the "Item
  Sites by Class Code" option. The following screen will appear:</para>
  <para>
<screenshot>
      <mediaobject>
        <imageobject>
          <imagedata fileref="images/IM_Disp_itemSitesByClass.png" id="Graphic549940"/>
        </imageobject>
        <caption id="Caption549943">Item Sites by Class Code</caption>
      </mediaobject>
    </screenshot>
</para>
  <para>When displaying Item Sites by Class Code, you are
  presented with the following options:</para>
  <variablelist>
    <varlistentry>
      <term>All Class Codes</term>
      <listitem id="listitemN0x180ac00N0x1932edc">
        <para>Select to display Item Sites for all Class Codes.</para>
      </listitem>
    </varlistentry>
    <varlistentry>
      <term>Selected</term>
      <listitem id="listitemN0x180ac00N0x1932f24">
        <para>Specify Class Code whose Item Sites you want to display.</para>
      </listitem>
    </varlistentry>
    <varlistentry>
      <term>Pattern</term>
      <listitem id="listitemN0x180ac00N0x1932f6c">
        <para>Enter a Class Code pattern to select a range of Class
        Codes.</para>
        <para>Refine your search using Regular Expressions, as
        described in <xref endterm="Anchor77806" linkend="Anchor77806"/>
    FINDME
  "Topic: Pattern Matching with Regular
        Expressions".</para>
      </listitem>
    </varlistentry>
    <varlistentry role="openmfg">
      <term>All Warehouses</term>
      <listitem id="listitemN0x180ac00N0x1932f90">
        <para>Select to display Item Sites by Class Code for all
        Warehouses.</para>
      </listitem>
    </varlistentry>
    <varlistentry role="openmfg">
      <term>Selected</term>
      <listitem id="listitemN0x180ac00N0x1932fb4">
        <para>Specify Warehouse whose Item Sites by Class Code you want to
        display.</para>
      </listitem>
    </varlistentry>
    <varlistentry>
      <term>Show Inactive</term>
      <listitem id="listitemN0x180ac00N0x1932ffc">
        <para>Select to display active as well as inactive Item Sites.</para>
      </listitem>
    </varlistentry>
    <varlistentry>
      <term>Item Sites</term>
      <listitem id="listitemN0x180ac00N0x1933044">
        <para>Display lists Item Sites by Class Code, using the specified
        parameters.</para>
      </listitem>
    </varlistentry>
  </variablelist>
  <para>To the far right of the screen, the following buttons
  are available:</para>
  <variablelist>
    <varlistentry>
      <term>CLOSE</term>
      <listitem id="listitemN0x180ac00N0x19330b0">
        <para>Closes the screen, returning you to the application
        desktop.</para>
      </listitem>
    </varlistentry>
    <varlistentry>
      <term>QUERY</term>
      <listitem id="listitemN0x180ac00N0x19330f8">
        <para>Select to generate the display, using the specified
        parameters.</para>
      </listitem>
    </varlistentry>
    <varlistentry>
      <term>PRINT</term>
      <listitem id="listitemN0x180ac00N0x1933140">
        <para>Runs the report associated with this screen.</para>
      </listitem>
    </varlistentry>
  </variablelist>
  <para>Right-clicking on an Item Site in the Item Sites list
  enables you to select from the following menu options:</para>
  <variablelist>
    <varlistentry>
      <term>View Item Site</term>
      <listitem id="listitem1">
        <para/>
      </listitem>
    </varlistentry>
    <varlistentry>
      <term>Edit Item Site</term>
      <listitem id="listitem2">
        <para/>
      </listitem>
    </varlistentry>
    <varlistentry>
      <term>View Inventory Availability</term>
      <listitem id="listitem3">
        <para/>
      </listitem>
    </varlistentry>
    <varlistentry>
      <term>Issue Count Tag</term>
      <listitem id="listitem4">
        <para/>
      </listitem>
    </varlistentry>
    <xi:include xmlns:xi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XInclude" href="../widgets/xtreewidget.xml" xpointer="element(xtreewidget.menu.exportcontents)"/>
  </variablelist>
</section>
